{
  "stem": "2723.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And indeed, a group of international Red Cross representatives were allowed at that stage, at that very late stage, into the camp.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "I don't know what they thought of us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "But I shudder to think how they possibly could think we were normal human beings.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "Naturally, we got nothing at the end of it, nothing at all.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "We were just left to the normal routine.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "But we did get a feeling things were coming to an end.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And then the day came, that fateful day-- I don't remember when it was-- when the Germans on the loud hailers told us that the camp is being vacated.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "They are leaving us there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "Um, those who want to live are to come with them to the next camp.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "The ones that are not going to work with them will be, um, killed.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And the killing was to be-- they showed us the detonators.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "They told us the whole camp was mined and we will be blasted into the air.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "And I think my decision was not just my decision.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "But a number of us could no longer face the ordeal.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "And we just decided-- chose to die.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "And that was it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "And we lay down in the gutter and waited for death to come.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They left us there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember, because somebody saw a clock in the office of the Germans.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was 2 o'clock in the afternoon.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that wait for that detonator was something I cannot describe.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I just kept thinking, my mother's done it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My sister's done it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Why am I so, um, afraid of death?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I guess I was, wafting in and out of consciousness, terrified.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But nothing happened.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
